name: JOKERS GROUP
briefDescription: JOKERS is a Non-Governmental Organization to promote welfare activities aimed at the alleviation of human suffering and overall amelioration of society especially for the poor, helpless youth/juveniles . The name JOKERS was carefully chosen to give a simple definition of the organization's activities.JOKERS stands for-JOYOFKINDNESS WITH THEEXPERIENCE OFRIGHT TIME HELP TOWARDSSOCIETY
